# Root .gitignore for AI-FinTech (Monorepo)
# ----------------------------------------

# Dependencies
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.next/
**/.out/
**/package-lock.json (exclude if you want to keep lock files, but typically kept)
# (Actually, package-lock should be kept)

# Environment variables & secrets
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Logs
**/logs/
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*

# Editor/System Files
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/*.suo
**/*.ntvs*
**/*.njsproj
**/*.sln
**/*.swp
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Misc
**/tmp/
**/temp/
**/.vercel/
**/.turbo/
